text: Lan padha ngelingana nali- kane sira lagi sathithik, dianggep apes ana ing nagara, kuwatir ma- nawa wong-wong padha amban- dhang sira, nanging Panjene- ngane angayomi sira sarta angu- kuhake sira kalawan pitulung-E tuwin apaparing sira arupa barang- barang becik, supaya sira padha atur panuwun
